1 of T itle 47 of the Oklahoma Statutes. The Department may apply for,
2 accept, and use any gift, grant, or bequest from any source for the
3 purpose of discharging its duties.
4 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2026.
5 COMMITTEE REPORT BY: COMMITTEE ON EDUCATION
